Computers do all sorts of things!

10
00:00:24,710 --> 00:00:28,800
Like transmitting sensitive data that’s
critical to national security,

11
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:32,529
which gets bounced around on servers throughout
the United States.

12
00:00:32,529 --> 00:00:35,359
With that in mind, maybe someone should have
realized

13
00:00:35,359 --> 00:00:39,800
it might be a problem that the backbone of
these computer networks

14
00:00:39,800 --> 00:00:42,170
is being built in China.

15
