16
00:00:43,170 --> 00:00:44,839
Oh wait, US intelligence agencies

17
00:00:44,839 --> 00:00:47,410
have been warning about this for years!

18
00:00:47,410 --> 00:00:49,749
But instead of listening to those intelligence
agencies—

19
00:00:49,749 --> 00:00:51,719
what do they know anyway?—

20
00:00:51,719 --> 00:00:55,120
a lot of major US companies ignored them,

21
00:00:55,120 --> 00:00:58,050
because who can say no to low prices?

22
00:00:58,050 --> 00:01:00,420
So these tech companies went for all the gold
that was

23
