26
00:01:08,090 --> 00:01:09,930
What do they have instead?

27
00:01:09,930 --> 00:01:12,630
Ok, that sounds painful.

28
00:01:12,630 --> 00:01:16,759
Yes, it turns out, the relentless pursuit
of cheaper products

29
00:01:16,759 --> 00:01:19,810
had a horrible, horrible downside.

30
00:01:19,810 --> 00:01:22,520
At least according to this Bloomberg article.

31
00:01:22,520 --> 00:01:27,190
It says China used microchips to infiltrate
US companies.

32
00:01:27,190 --> 00:01:29,050
This is a server motherboard.

33
00:01:29,050 --> 00:01:30,390
Get a bunch of these together,

34
00:01:30,390 --> 00:01:32,120
