201
00:08:19,259 --> 00:08:21,900
And that China, too, is a “victim of cybercrime.”

202
00:08:21,900 --> 00:08:24,650
And you can’t blame a victim!

203
00:08:24,650 --> 00:08:27,460
The Department of Homeland Security sort of
backed up

204
00:08:27,460 --> 00:08:29,780
Apple and Amazon’s denial, saying they,

205
00:08:29,780 --> 00:08:33,730
